Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.39,0:01:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Takashi and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:37.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fireflies are flying, right? They'll fly today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.89,0:01:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course they'll fly! We in the Firefly Club \Nhave raised larvae for a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already June though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:51.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're already flying everywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps they won't fly this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what went wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all worked so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe they'll fly if we wait a little bit longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waiting any longer isn't gonna do no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Playing catch-ball is more fun than fireflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.89,0:02:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Takashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:25.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Catch! {sore}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice ball!{guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.59,0:02:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There! {sore}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.95,0:02:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taka-kun, Akira-kun! \NIsn't it the Firefly Club day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! Welcome back, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're done with the whole Firefly Club thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:43.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, the teacher said the fireflies \Nmay not fly this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:54.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I so wanted to see the fireflies you raised fly about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:03:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, when I was about your age, \Nthe fireflies actually saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fireflies saved you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:13.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, Japan was waging war against China back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, a country called Manchukuo was forcibly created \Nin what is now the northeastern region of China,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where a great many of Japanese families were living.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Japan lost the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So a lot of children got separated from their families \Nand were left behind in China. {/parents and siblings}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was myself on the verge of not being able to return to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then, me and my family \Nlived in a Chinese city called Dalian.
