Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, sit quiet now, will you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish I could see dad sooner...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Almost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, on the day we arrived at Rason, \Nthe Soviet-Japanese war broke out.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.30,0:04:24.63,SIGNS,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF8F9E6&\fnBebas\blur0.502\fade(50,0)\fs18.075\frz1.349\fscx110\fscy107\pos(134.97,300)}Rason
