Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.30,0:04:24.63,SIGNS,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF8F9E6&\fnBebas\blur0.502\fade(50,0)\fs20.083\pos(421.066,172.654)}SOVIET
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:24.63,SIGNS,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2C2D27&\fnUnder\blur0.502\fade(50,0)\\fs85.354\frz355.4\pos(422.49,176.98)}b
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And because the Soviet army was in the immediate vicinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had to immediately turn back to Dalian \Nwithout ever getting a chance to see father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, are we going all the way to Dalian on this freight car?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:38.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were lucky to catch any ride at all. \NYou should bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You hang in there too, Hiro-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a little more. Bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't, I can't! I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:48.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The enemy is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no telling if it doesn't come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way, let's try going outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, Chisato and Hiroshi, \Nhold tight to mom, will you?{unsure what she means}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:25.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,, Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, mom! Why did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is just what war is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:49.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The train kept going for another two days towards Dalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, are we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:15.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more. Stay strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we get do Dalian, I can meet up \Nwith my friends again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, so—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The railway track is busted! {gues, no clue about second half}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no hope of fixing it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:37.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, take my hand! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dalian shouldn't be all that far by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys want to get home soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's keep our chins up \Nand push through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:13.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, even after we walked for two days straight, \Nthe city of Dalian still wasn't in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People camped on the ground as it became dark, {/slept}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then started walking again at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a repetition of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:10.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like we're borrowing \Nthis place's hospitality for tonight. {no clue why she says "rent and rest" there}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A farmer agreed to share it with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:22.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll split it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm starving already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, Hiro-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, Chi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you, mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is your share for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Eat up now, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw something over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, what are you doing out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:12.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! Sit with us and eat some.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Being all alone out here in the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be very difficult for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Feel free to rest here with us for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:44.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Shibata Yoshikazu-kun, right? {assuming she read the name on his school uniform}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did well to come this far all by yourself. \NA commendable feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father was killed by the enemy airplane attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother also got wounded. Later...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Chinese lady was looking after my mother and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I left mother behind and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your mother must be awfully worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like she'd ever worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's not even my real mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she was the one who raised you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, you're welcome to stay and rest here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope this rekindles your determination \Nto keep doing your best, together with your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think Yoshikazu-kun should return to Dalian with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know, his poor mother is injured and can't travel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:58.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She only has Yoshikazu-kun to rely upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Yoshikazu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma'am... Thank you... I... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshikazu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to where mother is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll manage to return to Japan, Yoshikazu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's meet up someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:25.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure. I'll never forget you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A marble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:50.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye! Stay safe, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, we should get going too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:07.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone started crossing over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:15:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! Just a bit further! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's cross over too. \NWe'll be at Dalian as soon as we cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right. If you muster all of your courage, we can cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to return home soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, we're almost through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mo—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:48.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please! Help!{guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to mom and Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die out here all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A firefly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:17:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, how pretty it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so gentle, so warm. Feels nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshikazu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshikazu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.61,0:18:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshikazu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:41.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshikazu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he can't hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:45.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chi-chan. Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:52.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the Forest of Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Forest of Life?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:56.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No need to be so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:19:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is a gathering spot \Nfor all the kind souls that value life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrapped in a kind soul, \Nany and all things can be restored. {no clue what he means at this point, just trying to sound fairy-tail-ish;}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:11.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, just like this forest, they can all live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then there's no war in this forest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:23.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, precisely so!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such a small firefly, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be it even just for a short spell, until the very-very end, \Nit'll shine the light of its life as best it can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As best it can... The light of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as the light of my life shines, \NI must keep doing my best too, just like the fireflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm never alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:52.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Came to my senses in a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for the fireflies coming to the riverside back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the fireflies saved you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:09.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fireflies granted me the strength to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:13.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how I realized that the Forest of Life \Nalways exists in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you have a kind heart, \Nyou can live in peace anywhere in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In my heart too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Forest of Life is a stunningly beautiful forest, \Nbrimming with fireflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, mom, now I wanna go to that forest too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can go there! \NIf kind hearts come together to protect all the life,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the whole world will be transformed \Ninto a Forest of Life where everyone can live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fireflies won't fly this year! \NDidn't I tell you it's pointless?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that, just come!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna! I quit the Firefly club, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.01,0:22:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't quit! You worked hard with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.59,0:22:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever it takes, I gotta show it to my mom!{no clue why he is pushing the fat guy there}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.45,0:22:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To my late father too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akira, fireflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.25,0:22:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fireflies are flying. They flew!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.57,0:22:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.82,0:22:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fireflies flew!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.62,0:23:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In my heart too,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.85,0:23:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there is the Forest of Life!
